Day 42: Create a Docker Network

Date: October 7, 2025
Overview
Set up Docker networks for container communication.
Key Concepts Learned

Bridge networks
Network isolation
Container DNS resolution
Network drivers

Commands Used
bashdocker network create my-network
docker network ls
docker run --network=my-network --name container1 image
docker network inspect my-network
Challenges Faced
Understanding network drivers and when to use custom networks vs default bridge.
